  "texts": [
    "To address this diversity, adaptive AI models must be developed that can account for these subjective factors and tailor predictions to individual preferences.",
    "Such models could integrate cultural datasets and user feedback loops to enhance relevance and acceptance across diverse populations.",
    "(2) Limited Dataset Diversity.",
    "Many existing sensory datasets lack adequate demographic, geographic, and cultural diversity.",
    "This limitation can restrict the generalizability of AI models and undermine their performance when applied across different populations."
  ]
